{"tid":1114671,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【夢幻對決】「杏目」下一目標： 安田紀念賽截擊「美麗傳承」！","createTime":"2019-04-18T15:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T15:53:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dbf00e8382d67bd3ee9c7a7d58bb162ea98bf8bb","tid":1114671,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T15:05:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20190418/59502074\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190418%2F59502074&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=4e65984d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190418%2F59502074&h=74e83f63\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20190418/59502074</a><br />\n<br />\n【夢幻對決】「杏目」下一目標： 安田紀念賽截擊「美麗傳承」！<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n昨天（18日）日本一口馬主團體絲綢會發表聲明，指「杏目」將不會以凱旋門大賽作為目標，令日本馬迷大失所望，練馬師國枝榮其後再現身作進一步解畫。<br />\n<br />\n國枝榮表示，其實「杏目」自日本橡樹大賽起，其後四次賽後均有不同程度的中暑跡象，情況令人相當擔心，因此他傾向避免遠行以免加重馬匹負擔。<br />\n<br />\n他其後補充，現時「杏目」下仗最有機會出戰6月2日1600米一級賽安田紀念賽，而練者對上一匹三冠馬后「夏威夷鳥」當年亦有出戰此賽，最後敗於頭馬「實際影響」跑第六。<br />\n<br />\n假如「杏目」果真成行，牠將有望與香港馬王「美麗傳承」上演夢幻一戰。「美麗傳承」將於4月28日衛冕冠軍一哩賽，馬主郭浩泉曾表示馬匹如能順利贏出，將很大機會入選安田紀念賽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190418/large/1555567046_3923.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190418%2Flarge%2F1555567046_3923.jpg&h=d05b393e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杏目（右）有望出師安田紀念賽，對撼美麗傳承。<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------<br />\n星期一至五晚上10點半<br />\n《動腦Q》Let's Q the money！<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2QW8LcI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QW8LcI&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=b428d094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2QW8LcI</a> <br />\n<br />\n---------------------------<br />\n4月18日 10am-11pm<br />\n玩《MINI GAME大挑戰》<br />\n贏取價值$140 QV潤膚乳液<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WigzsG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WigzsG&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=5b09366c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WigzsG</a>  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【從化開倉】將來增加十駒！羅富全：我可練到更多好馬<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【無奈身體唔爭氣】名字各有氣勢！兩四歲馬復活節前告退"},{"pid":"4c716db01f2441a8ab45c6b39fab733af8cce0c4","tid":1114671,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T15:06:19.000Z","msg":"依家邊隻高分啲 ?"},{"pid":"b42539e91f8d9227194ffe38197a6710c259cd5d","tid":1114671,"uid":35388,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c716db01f2441a8ab45c6b39fab733af8cce0c4","tid":1114671,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T15:06:19.000Z","msg":"依家邊隻高分啲 ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"美麗"},{"pid":"925e75c131efea95e3f7e1a5b8fb6e89181d580c","tid":1114671,"uid":184010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"唔知點解硬係覺得郭家唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a337817b0c4f86398db53b6493e8f61b9bf22664","tid":1114671,"uid":35365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"925e75c131efea95e3f7e1a5b8fb6e89181d580c","tid":1114671,"uid":184010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"唔知點解硬係覺得郭家唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T15:09:01.000Z","msg":"佢地肯定驚輸"},{"pid":"abc17453806e6ec82ec5f48d15e52bd1af395953","tid":1114671,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a337817b0c4f86398db53b6493e8f61b9bf22664","tid":1114671,"uid":35365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"925e75c131efea95e3f7e1a5b8fb6e89181d580c","tid":1114671,"uid":184010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4